{"tid":203070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[選後分裂]毓民怒批黃洋達 陳雲幫拖反擊:你返去泛民到吧!!","createTime":"2017-04-16T04:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T06:18:04.000Z","uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"688b337eefdd36fd4c5291cf9ec75da81c980a3d","tid":203070,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:29:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170415/19990901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170415%2F19990901&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=26cb3538\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170415%2F19990901&h=bcf0dd19\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170415/19990901</a><br />\n&ldquo;教主亦唔開名鬧埋選後大搞清黨嘅國師陳雲，同埋係咁喺fb block教主支持者嘅皇上黃洋達，指有人玩清黨「愈玩愈興奮，矛頭甚至指向MyRadio及我身邊的人」，令佢非常遺憾、又話有人連佢秘書喺fb上載同某啲人吃喝玩樂相，「竟然也不容於某位『敵我分明』的『面書』朋友」而被block，直言有人搞清算要寧枉毋縱，鬧呢啲人因為私怨、朋黨冇晒理性，「這樣的人還可以相信嗎？」&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n不出兩日，陳雲大反擊不點名怒插毓民<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/16/015509_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F16%2F015509_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=5c46ba86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n分裂已百熱化，大家又點睇呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25a404317b2dfdd647744b2c363e0334b26d18f","tid":203070,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T05:09:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcc0498e2e5fbdc63e15d28160806b8b2e2de227","tid":203070,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T05:14:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"837105e38d7f40eb865e5e29f8359234c6dc96df","tid":203070,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T05:30:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d86e44448e063d5